    {
      "id": "note_gt_constants",
      "type": "note",
      "label": "Ground truth & fixed constants",
      "position": {
        "x": 1203.6957786898597,
        "y": -788.0553407528084
      },
      "config": {
        "markdown": "**Ground truth & fixed constants** \u2014 full tables in `nodesets/method/voxposer/NOTES_ground_truth_and_constants.md`.\n\n**GT (not perceived)** \u2014 `env_libero__observe_objects` feeds a privileged MuJoCo snapshot: object names (BDDL), per-object **AABB** point clouds (boxes, not real geometry), EE pose, gripper state, workspace bounds.\n\n**Load-bearing constants**\n- Workspace z box: **per-scene from `robot0_base` z** (`_Z_BELOW_BASE=0.10` / `_Z_ABOVE_BASE=0.35`); x/y fixed `(-0.7,0.3)` / `(-0.4,0.5)`.\n- Gripper **action `+1`=close / `-1`=open** (the `-1=close` comments are stale).\n- OSC `_STEP_POS_M`=5mm/substep, `pos_tol`=5mm, `step_ee_pose.max_steps`=400.\n\n\u26a0\ufe0f **Table bug (fixed 2026-06-28)**: z box was hardcoded `[0.85,1.25]` (table-mounted spatial, base z\u22480.91). Floor-mounted `libero_object` (base z\u22480) sat ~0.9 m below \u2192 every grasp unreachable \u2192 object **0/50 for 29 AAS iters**. Fix \u2192 object **44/50 (0.88)**. Any z constant is a per-suite assumption \u2014 never re-hardcode."
      }
    }
